@@ -1,6 +1,6 @@

@@ -4890,16 +4890,16 @@
 
   "flag_pic"
   "*
-#ifdef HPUX_ASM
-  return \"bsr %0\";
-#else
 #ifdef MOTOROLA
   if (GET_CODE (operands[0]) == MEM 
       && GET_CODE (XEXP (operands[0], 0)) == SYMBOL_REF)
+#ifdef HPUX_ASM
+    return \"bsr.l %0\";
+#else
     return \"bsr %0@PLTPC\";
 #endif
-  return \"jsr %0\";
 #endif
+  return \"jsr %0\";
 ")
 
 ;; Call subroutine, returning value in operand 0
@@ -4945,16 +4945,16 @@
   ;; Operand 2 not really used on the m68000.
   "flag_pic"
   "*
-#ifdef HPUX_ASM
-  return \"bsr %1\";
-#else
 #ifdef MOTOROLA
   if (GET_CODE (operands[1]) == MEM 
       && GET_CODE (XEXP (operands[1], 0)) == SYMBOL_REF)
+#ifdef HPUX_ASM
+    return \"bsr.l %1\";
+#else
     return \"bsr %1@PLTPC\";
 #endif
-  return \"jsr %1\";
 #endif
+  return \"jsr %1\";
 ")
 
 ;; Call subroutine returning any type.
